ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 29th day of September, 2014, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED. The Petition for Writ of Mandamus and/or Extraordinary Relief is DENIED to the extent it requests extraordinary relief and GRANTED to the extent it requests mandamus relief. The court of common pleas is DIRECTED to adjudicate Petitioner’s pending filing within 90 days.
